## Priority Guide

| Priority | Meaning | When Claude Acts |
|----------|---------|------------------|
| **P0** | Urgent/Blocking | Immediately, before anything else |
| **P1** | Important | This session if time permits |
| **P2** | Normal | When relevant work is happening |
| **P3** | Low/Nice-to-have | When nothing else is pending |

